<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 01:04:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>通过嵌合抗原受体星形胶质细胞 (CAR-A) 疗法针对淀粉样蛋白 - β 病理学</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/targeting-amyloid-%ce%b2-pathology-by-chimeric-antigen-receptor-astrocyte-car-a-therapy</link><description>圣路易斯华盛顿大学的研究人员利用转基因星形胶质细胞（大脑中最丰富的细胞）开发了一种治疗阿尔茨海默病的新型细胞疗法。通过为这些细胞配备嵌合抗原受体（CAR），科学家们使它们能够特异性地靶向并清除β-淀粉样斑块，即在脑组织中积累并导致神经退行性变的有毒蛋白质沉积物。在小鼠试验中，单次注射可以防止年轻健康啮齿动物的斑块形成，并使年老小鼠现有的斑块水平减少一半。虽然该方法仍在完善以尽量减少副作用，并且必须评估人类安全性，但它有望作为阿尔茨海默氏症各个阶段的预防措施和治疗方法。通过重新编程细胞以靶向肿瘤标志物，相同的技术最终可能适用于癌症治疗。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/targeting-amyloid-ceb2-pathology-by-chimeric-antigen-receptor-astrocyte-car-a-therapy2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 01:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/targeting-amyloid-%ce%b2-pathology-by-chimeric-antigen-receptor-astrocyte-car-a-therapy</guid></item><item><title>MultiGen：扩散游戏引擎中可编辑多人世界的关卡设计</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/multigen-level-design-for-editable-multiplayer-worlds-in-diffusion-game-engines</link><description>想象一个视频游戏，它不仅在代码上运行，而且由人工智能实时“构思”——就像今天人工智能生成视频或图像的方式一样。虽然这项技术（称为扩散游戏引擎）非常令人兴奋，但它长期以来面临着两个主要障碍：一旦生成世界，你就无法轻松地“编辑”世界，并且你无法与朋友一起在那个世界中玩，因为人工智能无法同时为每个人保持一致的环境。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/multigen-level-design-for-editable-multiplayer-worlds-in-diffusion-game-engines3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 00:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/multigen-level-design-for-editable-multiplayer-worlds-in-diffusion-game-engines</guid></item><item><title>为什么有机体不仅仅是机器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-organisms-are-more-than-machines</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 00:34:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/why-organisms-are-more-than-machines</guid></item><item><title>生物学家布莱恩·韦尔姆将金属焊接到生物分子雕塑中</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/biologist-bryan-welm-welds-metals-into-biomolecular-sculptures</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 00:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/biologist-bryan-welm-welds-metals-into-biomolecular-sculptures</guid></item><item><title>在看似简单的“孤独跑步者”问题上取得了新的进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-strides-made-on-deceptively-simple-lonely-runner-problem</link><description>事实证明，关于跑步者绕跑道运动的简单猜想相当于许多复杂的数学问题。三个新的证明标志着几十年来该问题首次取得重大进展。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-strides-made-on-deceptively-simple-lonely-runner-problem.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 00:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-strides-made-on-deceptively-simple-lonely-runner-problem</guid></item><item><title>美国青少年补充和替代医学使用趋势</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/trends-in-complementary-and-alternative-medicine-use-among-us-youths</link><description>美国儿童的补充和替代医学使用率从 2007 年的 4.6% 上升到 2022 年的 17.7%，尤其是瑜伽和冥想，其中年轻群体的增幅最大。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/trends-in-complementary-and-alternative-medicine-use-among-us-youths2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 23:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/trends-in-complementary-and-alternative-medicine-use-among-us-youths</guid></item><item><title>创造更少迷幻、更有治疗作用的“神奇蘑菇”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/creating-less-trippy-more-therapeutic-magic-mushrooms</link><description>裸盖菇素——“迷幻蘑菇”中的精神活性化合物——因其在治疗神经精神疾病（包括抑郁症、焦虑症、药物滥用障碍和某些神经退行性疾病）方面的潜力而受到科学界的关注。然而，其致幻作用可能会限制更广泛的治疗应用。研究人员&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/creating-less-trippy-more-therapeutic-magic-mushrooms2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 23:34:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/creating-less-trippy-more-therapeutic-magic-mushrooms</guid></item><item><title>尽管总体有所改善，但 STEMI 患者院前延误率持续存在性别差异：来自中华心血管病协会胸痛中心登记处的调查结果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/persistent-sex-disparities-in-pre%e2%80%90hospital-delay-among-patients-with-stemi-despite-overall-improvements-findings-from-the-chinese-cardiovascular-association-chest-pain-center-registry</link><description>尽管整体情况有所改善，但中国患有 STEMI 的女性仍面临比男性更长的院前延误时间，尤其是在农村地区。这一差距主要是由于 EMS 呼叫延迟造成的。心脏病学。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/persistent-sex-disparities-in-pree28090hospital-delay-among-patients-with-stemi-despite-overall-improvements-findings-from-the-chinese-cardiovascular-association-chest-pain-center-registry2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 23:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/persistent-sex-disparities-in-pre%e2%80%90hospital-delay-among-patients-with-stemi-despite-overall-improvements-findings-from-the-chinese-cardiovascular-association-chest-pain-center-registry</guid></item><item><title>慢性鼻窦炎与癌症风险增加有关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/chronic-rhinosinusitis-tied-to-increased-cancer-risk</link><description>根据对亚洲患者的一项研究，慢性鼻窦炎可能与癌症风险增加有关。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/chronic-rhinosinusitis-tied-to-increased-cancer-risk.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 23:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/chronic-rhinosinusitis-tied-to-increased-cancer-risk</guid></item><item><title>摘要：干扰素信号传导在恶性周围神经鞘瘤放疗反应的关系中：</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/abstract-ifn-signaling-at-the-nexus-of-the-radiotherapy-response-in-malignant-peripheral-nerve-sheath-tumors</link><description>Sean P. Pitroda 和 Ralph R. Weichselbaum 对 Iowis Zhu 等人提供了评论。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/abstract95.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 22:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/abstract-ifn-signaling-at-the-nexus-of-the-radiotherapy-response-in-malignant-peripheral-nerve-sheath-tumors</guid></item></channel></rss>